metadata.Plot: A Marine Corps veteran suffering from PTSD takes his kids from California to Groom Lake, Nevada. He tells his children that alien parasites have landed on Earth to take over the planet. As their journey takes them in increasingly dangerous directions, the boys will need to leave their childhoods behind.
metadata.Actors: Riz Ahmed, Octavia Spencer, Lucian-River Chauhan
